1
00:00:21,840 --> 00:00:23,260
♪Wandering alone♪

2
00:00:23,260 --> 00:00:25,540
♪Walking far by dusk-lit streets♪

3
00:00:25,540 --> 00:00:27,430
♪Your eyes are as cold as clouds♪

4
00:00:27,430 --> 00:00:28,970
♪Faintly coming into view♪

5
00:00:28,970 --> 00:00:30,360
♪The city lights♪

6
00:00:30,360 --> 00:00:32,630
♪Lit up that single moment♪

7
00:00:32,630 --> 00:00:36,140
♪I can't hide or stop missing you♪

8
00:00:36,140 --> 00:00:37,640
♪I can't forget those moments♪

9
00:00:37,640 --> 00:00:39,280
♪Losing you♪

10
00:00:39,610 --> 00:00:41,320
♪Like the seasons in my memory♪

11
00:00:41,320 --> 00:00:43,290
♪Without winter♪

12
00:00:43,290 --> 00:00:44,920
♪Walking down the long, dark street♪

13
00:00:44,920 --> 00:00:46,460
♪Snow will never fall again♪

14
00:00:46,460 --> 00:00:48,200
♪Our old story was torn♪

15
00:00:48,200 --> 00:00:50,610
♪Into scattered pieces♪

16
00:00:50,610 --> 00:00:53,430
♪Replaying every single scene♪

17
00:00:53,430 --> 00:00:55,980
♪After you left♪

18
00:00:57,530 --> 00:01:00,510
♪As if our documentary♪

19
00:01:00,510 --> 00:01:03,120
♪Lost winter♪

20
00:01:04,770 --> 00:01:07,180
♪The breeze speaks of good times♪

21
00:01:07,180 --> 00:01:11,080
♪Pure white devotion♪

22
00:01:11,680 --> 00:01:13,990
♪Send out a letter♪

23
00:01:14,300 --> 00:01:17,780
♪Carrying my longing♪

24
00:01:17,780 --> 00:01:20,980
=The Double Game=

25
00:01:21,020 --> 00:01:23,940
=Episode 20=

26
00:01:26,340 --> 00:01:28,740
(2 hours before the livestream)

27
00:01:28,760 --> 00:01:29,780
Are you sure about this?

28
00:01:30,560 --> 00:01:31,460
Once this goes public,

29
00:01:31,950 --> 00:01:34,200
people online will talk about
and even curse

30
00:01:35,480 --> 00:01:37,680
your mom and grandpa.

31
00:01:38,870 --> 00:01:39,710
Aren't you scared?

32
00:01:40,680 --> 00:01:41,520
I am.

33
00:01:42,510 --> 00:01:44,000
But if we hide this so-called stain

34
00:01:44,840 --> 00:01:46,310
and let the guilty walk free,

35
00:01:46,603 --> 00:01:48,059
that would be the greatest disrespect

36
00:01:48,070 --> 00:01:49,070
to my mom and grandpa.

37
00:01:51,480 --> 00:01:52,510
They were victims too.

38
00:01:53,680 --> 00:01:54,950
Only by bringing out the truth

39
00:01:55,510 --> 00:01:57,230
can we give their spirits peace.

40
00:02:05,590 --> 00:02:06,430
Okay.

41
00:02:07,400 --> 00:02:08,240
I'm with you.

42
00:02:10,030 --> 00:02:11,030
I know a place

43
00:02:11,400 --> 00:02:12,826
that's perfect for this livestream.

44
00:02:13,960 --> 00:02:14,800
Let's go together

45
00:02:15,150 --> 00:02:16,240
and tell everyone the truth.

46
00:02:25,430 --> 00:02:26,520
Everyone in the livestream,

47
00:02:26,960 --> 00:02:28,840
(He'll pay)
Ms. Fang and Mr. Fang may have

48
00:02:29,066 --> 00:02:29,960
unintentionally helped

49
00:02:30,000 --> 00:02:32,310
(Wilder than a drama)
with the development permit,

50
00:02:32,750 --> 00:02:35,560
but they were victims in this too,

51
00:02:35,840 --> 00:02:37,470
and they lost their lives because of it.

52
00:02:37,710 --> 00:02:39,680
Lu Jianchuan

53
00:02:39,803 --> 00:02:41,463
(Clear their name)
was the one behind it.

54
00:02:41,520 --> 00:02:42,360
And that's not all.

55
00:02:42,910 --> 00:02:44,280
To cover up what he did,

56
00:02:44,710 --> 00:02:45,750
Lu Jianchuan even arranged

57
00:02:46,083 --> 00:02:47,783
the deaths of Lin Youqiang
and his family.

58
00:02:48,360 --> 00:02:49,360
He even tried to silence

59
00:02:49,470 --> 00:02:51,216
Jin Chanchan,
who was set to expose it all.

60
00:02:54,840 --> 00:02:56,120
It was a vile explosion plot.

61
00:02:56,840 --> 00:02:57,910
Jin Chanchan's twin sister

62
00:02:58,080 --> 00:03:00,680
was left comatose by accident.

63
00:03:01,400 --> 00:03:02,280
Nonsense.

64
00:03:02,710 --> 00:03:05,190
No proof means you're framing me.

65
00:03:07,470 --> 00:03:09,430
This is a fake
supporting facilities certificate.

66
00:03:12,840 --> 00:03:14,150
This is Fang Wenyuan's statement.

67
00:03:16,200 --> 00:03:17,629
This is the statement of Xu Wangzu,

68
00:03:17,640 --> 00:03:18,853
who was hired by Lu Jianchuan.

69
00:03:19,520 --> 00:03:21,680
Every piece of it is solid proof.

70
00:03:22,120 --> 00:03:23,280
Once this livestream is over,

71
00:03:23,750 --> 00:03:26,030
we'll hand every bit of evidence
to the police.

72
00:03:26,710 --> 00:03:29,120
The law will decide fairly.

73
00:03:31,030 --> 00:03:32,870
Causing trouble in my turf?

74
00:03:33,750 --> 00:03:34,680
You'll pay for this.

75
00:03:37,680 --> 00:03:38,520
Move.

76
00:03:39,560 --> 00:03:40,400
He's leaving?

77
00:03:42,543 --> 00:03:43,829
There's one more piece of proof.

78
00:03:44,680 --> 00:03:46,000
I'm sure you all saw it.

79
00:03:47,000 --> 00:03:48,750
Today's livestream room
is set up specially.

80
00:03:49,710 --> 00:03:50,550
Because this is

81
00:03:50,960 --> 00:03:51,910
where Lu Jianchuan

82
00:03:52,240 --> 00:03:54,120
locks up anyone who threatens him.

83
00:03:55,190 --> 00:03:56,240
Exactly.

84
00:03:56,630 --> 00:03:57,630
This is so cruel.

85
00:03:57,800 --> 00:03:58,640
I was

86
00:03:59,560 --> 00:04:00,960
once locked up here too.

87
00:04:02,430 --> 00:04:03,270
So,

88
00:04:03,910 --> 00:04:05,710
I want to use this place

89
00:04:06,680 --> 00:04:08,080
to put an end to all this evil.

90
00:04:33,310 --> 00:04:34,950
Lu Tingxiao, you ungrateful son!

91
00:04:35,870 --> 00:04:36,923
Let's see what you can do.

92
00:04:40,160 --> 00:04:41,310
What's happening?

93
00:04:43,160 --> 00:04:44,510
Who told you to livestream this?

94
00:04:44,950 --> 00:04:45,790
I...

95
00:04:47,310 --> 00:04:48,309
What are you waiting for?

96
00:04:48,360 --> 00:04:49,390
Go do what you need to do.

97
00:04:49,870 --> 00:04:51,000
Be a man for once.

98
00:04:51,390 --> 00:04:53,160
Lu Tingyu, you heartless traitor!

99
00:04:53,310 --> 00:04:54,469
You deserve to be cheated on.

100
00:04:57,560 --> 00:04:59,190
This isn't your place to act up.

101
00:04:59,780 --> 00:05:00,650
You...

102
00:05:00,680 --> 00:05:01,520
Let go.

103
00:05:03,560 --> 00:05:05,310
- Lu Tingxiao.
- Dad, stop now.

104
00:05:06,430 --> 00:05:07,760
- Tingyu.
- Dad.

105
00:05:08,070 --> 00:05:09,870
You two ungrateful sons.

106
00:05:10,480 --> 00:05:12,270
(He's furious)
Are you still my sons?

107
00:05:12,720 --> 00:05:13,560
It's back.

108
00:05:13,600 --> 00:05:14,510
The truth is out.

109
00:05:15,390 --> 00:05:16,480
Did you see that?

110
00:05:16,720 --> 00:05:17,920
This is the power of truth.

111
00:05:19,120 --> 00:05:21,120
It strips the mad of their mask

112
00:05:21,270 --> 00:05:23,240
and makes the just speak up.

113
00:05:24,190 --> 00:05:26,000
Thanks for watching today's livestream.

114
00:05:26,950 --> 00:05:29,160
Today, I took off the mask
and exposed the wrongs.

115
00:05:29,360 --> 00:05:31,360
From here on,
I'm still your Jin Chanchan.

116
00:05:32,160 --> 00:05:33,780
(You won't change)
The mask won't change

117
00:05:33,920 --> 00:05:34,800
my determination

118
00:05:34,920 --> 00:05:36,913
(We're with you)
to pursue the truth and justice.

119
00:05:37,270 --> 00:05:38,160
I'll keep calling out

120
00:05:38,920 --> 00:05:40,160
the evil.

121
00:05:40,160 --> 00:05:42,460
(You deserve it)

122
00:05:42,480 --> 00:05:43,320
Bye.

123
00:05:43,560 --> 00:05:45,030
- Nice job.
- Well said.

124
00:05:45,560 --> 00:05:46,400
That was well said.

125
00:05:49,660 --> 00:05:51,500
(Jin Chanchan Studio)

126
00:06:00,000 --> 00:06:00,840
Wen Yan,

127
00:06:01,270 --> 00:06:02,110
take a look.

128
00:06:02,190 --> 00:06:04,040
Your fans sent you a gift through me.

129
00:06:06,140 --> 00:06:08,420
(To: Jin Chanchan Studio,
Light of Justice)

130
00:06:08,420 --> 00:06:09,660
(From Fei Yifan, a kind citizen)

131
00:06:10,830 --> 00:06:12,000
Fei Yifan.

132
00:06:12,800 --> 00:06:13,640
How's he been lately?

133
00:06:14,310 --> 00:06:16,510
He said thanks for helping him
get his investment back.

134
00:06:16,950 --> 00:06:18,120
He's a lot more grounded now,

135
00:06:18,480 --> 00:06:19,680
focusing on his career.

136
00:06:20,040 --> 00:06:20,880
That's good.

137
00:06:21,240 --> 00:06:23,120
Let's hope he doesn't become
our target again.

138
00:06:25,120 --> 00:06:25,960
Bai,

139
00:06:26,000 --> 00:06:26,840
where's my gift?

140
00:06:30,270 --> 00:06:32,070
I didn't see any fans of yours.

141
00:06:37,870 --> 00:06:38,710
But

142
00:06:39,430 --> 00:06:40,830
I have two tickets

143
00:06:41,630 --> 00:06:42,480
for you.

144
00:06:42,720 --> 00:06:44,480
I just want gifts from my fans.

145
00:06:44,830 --> 00:06:45,670
They are from a fan.

146
00:06:45,830 --> 00:06:46,870
I'm your fan.

147
00:06:47,360 --> 00:06:49,360
I know you love this idol group,

148
00:06:49,720 --> 00:06:50,600
so I got two tickets

149
00:06:50,680 --> 00:06:51,720
to their concert.

150
00:06:59,040 --> 00:06:59,920
I've got stuff to do.

151
00:07:00,160 --> 00:07:01,070
I'm not going with you.

152
00:07:02,680 --> 00:07:04,390
If no one can go with you,

153
00:07:05,680 --> 00:07:06,680
I can go with you.

154
00:07:07,510 --> 00:07:08,350
Floor seats?

155
00:07:08,630 --> 00:07:09,870
How did you even get them?

156
00:07:20,720 --> 00:07:21,560
(Back then,)

157
00:07:22,390 --> 00:07:24,310
(I thought a career was just personal.)

158
00:07:25,750 --> 00:07:26,600
(Later, I realized)

159
00:07:27,360 --> 00:07:29,750
(a voice can truly spark echoes)

160
00:07:30,510 --> 00:07:31,630
(and move a giant stone,)

161
00:07:33,360 --> 00:07:35,040
(helping the trapped find a way out,)

162
00:07:35,950 --> 00:07:38,000
(and bringing buried truth to light.)

163
00:07:39,190 --> 00:07:40,360
(Every serious person)

164
00:07:40,950 --> 00:07:42,190
(is a small beam of light.)

165
00:07:43,680 --> 00:07:45,070
(When many beams come together,)

166
00:07:45,830 --> 00:07:46,720
(they can light up)

167
00:07:47,480 --> 00:07:48,750
(and change this world.)

168
00:07:51,720 --> 00:07:52,870
(Lin Zhi'er was discharged.)

169
00:07:54,160 --> 00:07:55,870
(She and Lu Tingyu divorced peacefully.)

170
00:08:00,000 --> 00:08:00,950
I hope that you'll get

171
00:08:01,950 --> 00:08:02,800
what you wish for.

172
00:08:04,430 --> 00:08:06,483
(Lu Tingyu convinced Xu Shulin
to turn herself in.)

173
00:08:07,480 --> 00:08:09,310
(Both of them started anew.)

174
00:08:10,680 --> 00:08:12,190
I'm finally leaving this place.

175
00:08:14,920 --> 00:08:15,760
I know I have

176
00:08:16,270 --> 00:08:17,800
no right to ask you for anything.

177
00:08:18,560 --> 00:08:19,950
You hate Luzhou Group,

178
00:08:21,310 --> 00:08:22,150
but

179
00:08:22,510 --> 00:08:25,160
it was built with your mother's effort.

180
00:08:26,160 --> 00:08:27,513
The company itself is not guilty.

181
00:08:28,240 --> 00:08:30,240
The guilty are those
who use it for evil.

182
00:08:31,510 --> 00:08:32,360
If possible,

183
00:08:33,000 --> 00:08:35,080
I hope you can save your mother's legacy

184
00:08:36,670 --> 00:08:38,000
and let it rise again.

185
00:08:40,000 --> 00:08:40,840
(Ending)

186
00:08:41,600 --> 00:08:43,030
(is for a new beginning.)

187
00:08:46,870 --> 00:08:49,150
(After the divorce,
Lu Tingyu decided to study abroad.)

188
00:08:51,150 --> 00:08:52,840
(Xu Shulin left with him.)

189
00:08:59,320 --> 00:09:01,440
(Lu Tingxiao met everyone's hopes)

190
00:09:02,600 --> 00:09:03,630
(and made bold changes)

191
00:09:03,840 --> 00:09:05,480
(to Luzhou Group.)

192
00:09:06,390 --> 00:09:08,720
(Lianxin Island's restoration began.)

193
00:09:09,440 --> 00:09:11,080
(All illegal buildings were torn down.)

194
00:09:12,440 --> 00:09:13,280
(By the way,)

195
00:09:13,670 --> 00:09:16,360
(he was also named
Entrepreneur of the Year.)

196
00:09:44,480 --> 00:09:46,150
(Justice isn't one person
charging ahead;)

197
00:09:47,120 --> 00:09:48,960
(it's having someone
with you through it all)

198
00:09:49,670 --> 00:09:51,200
(and someone guarding your back.)

199
00:09:52,670 --> 00:09:54,270
(Lin Zhi'er found herself again.)

200
00:09:55,440 --> 00:09:57,030
(Lu Tingyu found his way.)

201
00:09:58,120 --> 00:09:59,750
(Lu Tingxiao washed off the dust.)

202
00:10:01,240 --> 00:10:02,080
(And I)

203
00:10:02,910 --> 00:10:04,790
(was no longer
the lonely little elephant.)

204
00:10:05,840 --> 00:10:07,790
(I had someone to watch the sea with.)

205
00:10:19,200 --> 00:10:20,320
(Lu Jianchuan was convicted)

206
00:10:20,320 --> 00:10:21,549
(of unlawful detention, fraud,)

207
00:10:21,560 --> 00:10:22,141
(and bribery.)

208
00:10:22,260 --> 00:10:22,850
(Lin Yuqing)

209
00:10:22,850 --> 00:10:23,490
(and Xu Shulin)

210
00:10:23,490 --> 00:10:24,223
(were also found)

211
00:10:24,234 --> 00:10:25,223
(guilty of their crimes.)

212
00:10:38,900 --> 00:10:40,350
♪This door♪

213
00:10:40,750 --> 00:10:45,500
♪Lets in the sky outside♪

214
00:10:45,980 --> 00:10:49,540
♪With a voice even lighter♪

215
00:10:49,540 --> 00:10:52,350
♪Than how you just greeted me♪

216
00:10:52,800 --> 00:10:54,170
♪I know now♪

217
00:10:54,500 --> 00:10:59,380
♪What the chill in my body means♪

218
00:10:59,730 --> 00:11:02,600
♪The moment salt hits the wound♪

219
00:11:02,800 --> 00:11:06,220
♪My heart still beats so naively♪

220
00:11:06,390 --> 00:11:09,380
♪To complete♪

221
00:11:09,840 --> 00:11:13,590
♪A joy that needs no brave pretense♪

222
00:11:13,730 --> 00:11:16,230
♪How cruel sincerity can be♪

223
00:11:16,370 --> 00:11:19,920
♪Like a door with no key♪

224
00:11:20,230 --> 00:11:22,550
♪Maybe you just passed by♪

225
00:11:22,550 --> 00:11:26,130
♪The tears in my eyes♪

226
00:11:26,840 --> 00:11:29,390
♪You looked like you had nothing to say♪

227
00:11:29,390 --> 00:11:31,130
♪Then got so good at being cold♪

228
00:11:31,130 --> 00:11:33,970
♪That's why a smile feels so precious♪

229
00:11:34,180 --> 00:11:36,270
♪Maybe you just passed by♪

230
00:11:36,420 --> 00:11:40,750
♪The tears burned into my heart♪

231
00:11:41,130 --> 00:11:43,420
♪Let's say silence was just for show♪

232
00:11:43,420 --> 00:11:48,090
♪Even if I've grown another year♪
